keyMappings:
unmap J
unmap K
unmap X
unmap d
unmap gT
unmap gt
unmap t
unmap u
unmap x

map <c-b> scrollFullPageUp
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-f> scrollFullPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
map d removeTab
map t$ lastTab
map t0 firstTab

map td removeTab
map tn nextTab
map tp previousTab
map tu restoreTab
map u restoreTab
